Class FGSolvingStrategy

java.lang.Object
fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.strategies.im.AbstractIMSolvingStrategy

All Implemented Interfaces:
SolvingStrategyInterface
public class FGSolvingStrategy extends AbstractIMSolvingStrategy
Solving strategy Frequent Generator Itemsets. A (frequent) itemset 𝑋 is a generator if there exists no (frequent) itemset 𝑌 such that 𝑌 ⊂ 𝑋 and sup(𝑋) = sup(Y). See this course by Philippe Fournier Viger for more information.

  • Method Details

    • solve

      public Solutions<ItemSet> solve(String filePath) throws IOException, InstantiationException
      Default method to be used by every concrete Itemset Mining (IM) strategy. It checks whether an algorithm name is defined, if so, it gets that algorithm, if not it gets the default algorithm for said concrete FMI strategy.
      Specified by:
      solve in interface SolvingStrategyInterface
      Overrides:
      solve in class AbstractIMSolvingStrategy
      Parameters:
      filePath - path to the transactional database file.
      Returns:
      The frequent generator itemsets as solutions.
      Throws:
      IOException - All other problems whilst running the algorithm, etc.
      InstantiationException - Whether there is a problem when creating the runner used in the solving strategy.
